        <mxCell id="boundary" value="Boundary contract&#xa;1. Adapter signs every WorldEvent with its plugin keypair.&#xa;2. Adapter consumes Actions and returns ActionResult.&#xa;3. No shared state — neither side writes to the other&apos;s DB.&#xa;4. Independent failure domains — OpenClaw down ≠ CoreMind down." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#999;align=left;fontSize=10" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="680" width="780" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

